no longer fear death.

00:21.480 --> 00:23.391
What I fear...

00:24.858 --> 00:26.940
is a fruitless death.

00:28.153 --> 00:29.188
(sniffles)

00:29.279 --> 00:31.941
What I ask for...

00:32.031 --> 00:34.899
after you have given me so much...

00:38.539 --> 00:40.906
