06:41.234 --> 06:44.443
Tell me where to go and what to do,
I'll make it happen.

06:44.529 --> 06:46.486
(chuckles)

06:50.201 --> 06:52.033
(door opens, closes)

06:52.120 --> 06:55.454
Where were we, Gregory?
Oh, that's right.

06:55.540 --> 06:58.248
You were telling me
that you don't like to kill people,

06:58.335 --> 07:02.044
and I was saying that I do...

07:02.130 --> 07:04.713
under the right circumstances.

07:04.799 --> 07:06.585
Well, this-- this situation

07:06.676 --> 07:08.132
that we-- we find ourselves in,

07:08.219 --> 07:10.210
